## DBsubject(Trigonometry)
## DBchapter(Triangle trigonometry)
## DBsection(Sine, cosine, and tangent of an angle in a right triangle)
## Date(01/01/10)
## Institution(Fort Lewis College)
## Author(Paul Pearson)
## Level(2)
## MO(1)
